V1 IN 0 12
C6 0 DRVCC 10µ
C2 OUT 0 100µ x2 Rser=5m
C1 OUT 0 100µ x2 Rser=2m
V3 CLK_EXT 0 PULSE(0 5 1.8m 1n 1n 500n 1u 500)
C8 CLK_EXT SYNC/PWM_CFG 1.5n
R2 SYNC/PWM_CFG 0 162k
R3 EXTVCC _ALERT 100k
R1 EXTVCC PGOOD 100k
C5 0 VDD18 4.7µ
C7 0 INTVCC 10µ
V2 RUN 0 PWL(500u 0 500.001u 5 2500u 5 2500.001u 0)
L1 SW OUT 470n Rser=2.5m
V4 EXTVCC 0 5
X§U1 IN SW 0 SW BOOST BOOST DRVCC INTVCC EXTVCC VDD18 _ALERT 0 OUT 0 RUN PGOOD 0 SYNC/PWM_CFG LT7170 FREQUENCY_SWITCH=750k VOUT_RANGE=0 VOUT_COMMAND=0.85 VIN_ON= 1.4 VIN_OFF=1.35 TON_DELAY=.01m TON_RISE=.5m TOFF_DELAY=.2m TOFF_FALL=.3m ILIM_RANGE=0 GMEA_CONTROL=10 RITH=7k CITH=320p MFR_PWM_PHASE=180 VOUT_UV_FAULT_LIMIT=0.6 VOUT_OV_FAULT_LIMIT=1 VOUT_UV_WARN_LIMIT=0.5 VOUT_OV_WARN_LIMIT=0.9 MFR_DISCHARGE_THRESHOLD=0.2
C3 BOOST SW 0.1µ
S1 0 OUT N001 0 Rload
V5 N001 0 PULSE(0 8 1.2m 100n 100n 300u)
.tran 3.5m startup
* The following parameters can be defined by right-clicking on the LT7170 symbol.\n \nFrequency_switch -- in Hz, sets switching frequency\n \nVout_range -- sets maximum output range, 0 for 1.375V, 1 for 2.75V, 2 for 5.5V\n \nVout_command -- in volt, sets output voltage\n \nTon_delay & Ton_rise -- in sec, set ON delay and soft-start time\nToff_delay & Toff_fall -- in sec, set OFF delay and soft-off time \n \nIlim_range -- sets current limit options:\n     0 positive valley current limit of 9A per phase, negative valley current limit of -6A\n   1 positive valley current limit of 13A per phase, negative valley current limit of -7.6A\n   2 positive valley current limit of 15.6A per phase, negative valley current limit of -9.4A\n   3 positive valley current limit of 21.4A per phase, negative valley current limit of -12A \n \nGMEA_control--Sets Error Amp parameters, N=0 to 31\nGmEA = 0.15mS*(n+1)/(2^VOUT_RANGE)    (relative to VSENSE inputs)\n ImaxOutEA = 8.5uA*(n+1) \n \nRITH--in ohm, programmable internal compensation\n \nCITH--in Farad, programmable internal compensation\nMFR_PWM_PHASE-- in degree, sets the master phase delay in 15-degree increments with respect to the SYNC frequency if present.\nVout_UV_Fault_Limit and Vout_OV_Fault_Limit --- in volt, set the undervoltage and overvoltage fault limit for the Pgood output\nVout_UV_Warn_Limit and Vout_OV_Warn_Limit-- in volt, set the undervoltage and overvoltage warning limit for the Alert output\nMFR_PWM_THRSHOLD, Output voltage threshold to determine that the output has decayed sufficiently to reenable the channel
.model Rload SW( Ron={0.85/8} Roff={0.85/1} Vt=0.5 Vh=-0.45)
.lib LT7170.sub
